<H3> <TI>   Police Arrest Man With Radioactive Material </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD2102181194 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1656 GMT 21 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2102181194 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


