<F P=106> [From "News Bulletin" No. 33/94] </F>
  [Text] The Customs Service discovered a container with 
radioactive scrap metal in a Tallinn commercial port storage 
yard on Tuesday [15 February]. The radiation level exceeds the 
maximum permitted level ten times. The Rescue Service is to 
remove the container today. 

