Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Nikolay Yefimovich report: "Radioactive Train"] </F>
  [Text] Several containers of Polonium-210 have been seized 
from the transport network by staffers of the Volga-Vyatka 
Internal Affairs Administration. The newspaper NIZHEGORODSKIYE 
NOVOSTI reports that the unusual contraband had been despatched 
