<H3> <TI>   Scientific Center to Monitor China's Lob Nor Nuclear Range </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1003172294 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 1200 GMT 
10 Mar 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1003172294 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow Mayak Radio Network </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Russian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The laboratory of atmospheric processes of the 
Kyygyzstan Academy of Sciences' Physics Institute has been 
tasked with monitoring the effects of activity at the Chinese 
Lob Nor nuclear testing range on the neighboring territories in 
Kyrgyzstan. 
  A RIA correspondent has learned at the government press 
service that an agreement to this effect was signed today 
between the Academy of Sciences and the republican government's 
State Commission for Emergency Situations and Civil Defense. 

</TEXT>

